rows.label: tev900191_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, hey, it's you. Something the matter?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0020
rows.name: Huh? Why am I wearing the helmet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0030
rows.name: Isn't it obvious? ...It's comfy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0040
rows.name:
I don't have to squint with the sunlight,
and there's climate control inside the suit
so it stays at just the right temperature.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0050
rows.name:
Not to mention it looks cool.
What more could you want?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_JNK0070
rows.name: Ingratiate

rows.label: tev900191_SEL0080
rows.name: Admit that Liesel does rock the look.

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0090
rows.name:
I know looks aren't everything,
but as a test pilot, I'm kind of like a
walking billboard for the product.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0100
rows.name:
I keep telling folks I should get paraded around
in full gear, but for some reason they always
shoot the idea down...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0110
rows.name:
Ah well. It isn't easy being on the
bleeding edge of fashion. The rest
of the world needs time to catch up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0120
rows.name:
But once they do, all Skell pilots
everywhere will be wearing this.
Mark my words.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0130
rows.name:
I'm telling you, I believe in its potential,
one hundred percent. You should try it
yourself, if you get the chance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_JNK0140
rows.name: Scathe

rows.label: tev900191_SEL0150
rows.name: Question her aesthetic sense.

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0160
rows.name:
...Hm? Oh, sorry, I was just getting some
static. Did you say something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0170
rows.name:
The external mics have been a bit temperamental.
I'll have to get Leesh to take a look later...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0180
rows.name:
I don't think I've mentioned before, but
this suit is one of a kind. Alicia designed
and made it especially for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0190
rows.name:
In particular the helmet. She sweated over
the design for days on end before landing
on this one. She says it really suits me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0200
rows.name:
Hah. Leesh is a genius when it comes to
this kinda stuff. As her bestie, I'm proud,
and I don't mind gushing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0210
rows.name:
Oh, sorry, I just steamed right over you.
What was it you were saying earlier?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0220
rows.name:
...Hm? Nothing?
Well, okay, if you say so...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_JNK0230
rows.name: Opine

rows.label: tev900191_SEL0240
rows.name: Admit you find it cute.

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0250
rows.name:
Cute? Hmm... Okay...?
Cute, huh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0260
rows.name:
I don't know how else to put it, so I'll just
come out and say it: If you think this is
cute, then I doubt your aesthetic sense.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0270
rows.name:
No matter how you slice it, it's got
wildness, it's got mischief... All qualities
you'd associate with "cool."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900191_MSG0280
rows.name:
...No, wait, I'm sorry. I shouldn't have
said that. Aesthetics are a very subjective
topic. Please forget I said anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: NewText_29
rows.name: Finally, Liezel favorability increased
